</ul>
<p><a name="Government" id="Government"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Intelligent_transportation_system&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20" title="Edit section: Government">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Government</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.its.dot.gov/" class="external text" title="http://www.its.dot.gov/" rel="nofollow">United States Department of Transportation, Research and Innovative Technology Administration, Intelligent Transportation Systems Joint Program Office</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.its-australia.com.au" class="external text" title="http://www.its-australia.com.au" rel="nofollow">Australian ITS Source - 1 terabyte library website ITS research</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.mlit.go.jp/road/ITS/" class="external text" title="http://www.mlit.go.jp/road/ITS/" rel="nofollow">Japanese Government ITS Program</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.iot.gov.tw/its/mp.asp" class="external text" title="http://www.iot.gov.tw/its/mp.asp" rel="nofollow">ITS Program of Institute of Transportation, Ministry of Transportation and Communications, Republic of China (Taiwan)</a></li>
</ul>
