<p><a name="Education" id="Education"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Intelligent_transportation_system&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: Education">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Education</span></h4>
<ul>
