<li><a href="http://www.njtide.org" class="external text" title="http://www.njtide.org" rel="nofollow">Cooperative traffic systems lab of</a> <a href="/wiki/Rutgers_University" title="Rutgers University">Rutgers</a>, <a href="/wiki/Princeton_University" title="Princeton University">Princeton</a>, and the <a href="/wiki/New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology" title="New Jersey Institute of Technology">New Jersey Institute of Technology</a></li>
