<li><a href="http://www.lith.liu.se/en/master/its.html" class="external text" title="http://www.lith.liu.se/en/master/its.html" rel="nofollow">Master's Programme in Intelligent Transport Systems, Linköpings universitet</a></li>
<li><a href="http://cvrr.ucsd.edu/lisa/" class="external text" title="http://cvrr.ucsd.edu/lisa/" rel="nofollow">Laboratory for Intelligent and Safe Automobiles, University of California, San Diego</a></li>
